{"tid":638277,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★[World No IT]美國司法部：No more eSIM 研發！","createTime":"2018-04-22T14:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-22T14:52:14.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6583aac3be149a83c05180fdd648734e8939bb3c","tid":638277,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:46:32.000Z","msg":"目前我們手機中都會加入 SIM 卡作為連接流動網絡的記認，不過這個技術已經相當古老，有關方面早就着手研發可內置手機中的 eSIM，不過最近卻遇到障礙。<br />\n<br />\n負責制訂電訊規格的 GSM 協會近年一直在研究 eSIM 統一規格，不過<span style=\"color: red;\">最近宣佈進度需要暫停，因為美國司法部正在針對 AT&amp;T、Verizon 和 GSM 協會合謀窒礙 eSIM 發展事宜展開調查</span>。雖然 eSIM 可以減少更換 SIM 卡的麻煩並節省手機體積，但電訊商一向對 eSIM 不太熱衷，因為會令客戶更易流失。<br />\n<br />\n今次美國司法部的調查就是檢查電訊商如果與 GSM 協會合作，是否會有利於捆綁客戶，從而影響市場競爭和可能違反美國的反壟斷法。目前 eSIM 雖然未有統一規範，但在部分產品如 Apple Watch 和 Google Pixel 2 等都已經有採用。今次 GSM 協會遇到麻煩，相信在主流產品中普及使用 eSIM 仍然有很長的距離。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/04/22/gsma-puts-esim-on-hold-due-to-us-investigation/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F04%2F22%2Fgsma-puts-esim-on-hold-due-to-us-investigation%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=rwHfFTi%2BbPbufjMtzjzA%2BsP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=7b2bc40f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/04/22/gsma-puts-esim-on-hold-due-to-us-investigation/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"e0e3ae291a23b482af98fd9b53935a9c538d0475","tid":638277,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695eeb49ed04bb780c68a8b2b4521a633b355cc3","tid":638277,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-22T14:47:17.000Z","msg":"trump hate IT"},{"pid":"41cf6133e508e40fd0ff2445dd7b22de5396e000","tid":638277,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc